OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with a few showers.
OL,7,FOvernight there will be variable
OL,8,Famounts of cloud with clear spells but
OL,9,Falso a few more showers.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAny early showers soon dying
OL,12,Fout. Then the rest of the day will be
OL,13,Fdry with sunny spells.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry,
OL,16,Fbright and warm on Sunday. Mainly dry,
OL,17,Fbright and very warm on Monday,
OL,18,Fperhaps the odd shower. Clouider on
OL,19,FTuesday with the odd shower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
